title: breadcrumbs

needs:
 - slice of bread
 - salt
 - pepper

steps:
 - slice the bread into small chunks.
 - grind the chunks into smaller pieces.
 - add some salt and pepper.
 - spread the chunks out on a tray.
 - dry the chunks in the oven for 5-ish minutes.
 - take them out, grind them again.
 - maybe put them back in the oven if they're still moist.
